N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 19 ยง 204.18 - Change in approved course of study

State Regulations

There shall be no change or alteration in any approved course
of study, of any subject, in any instruction staff or course provider without
prior written notice and approval by the division. Notes
